channel.title: ◙[REQUEST]◙ Website Banner / Header
channel.description:
So I currently have a banner. Someone else that had offered to create me a new one did, but I'm not that interested because it just doesn't match my website / forum. Anyway I'm not picky at all and I'm willing to pay, I just need a quick but efficiently thrown together header that's better than my old one. No requirements needed, just create your own thing and post or pm me, and if you want paid I'll pay.
[b]Old one: [/b]
http://prntscr.com/4u41tt
Please, and thank you.
